title: Par 6 (2002)
description:
A cynical man returns to his family's homestead in Texas and starts up a golf course with his brothers and sisters.  



As far as I can tell, there is only one existent copy of this movie in the world. It was a VHS which was dubbed onto DVD and then sold on ebay to a tumblr user, who ripped it and began distributing it via assorted file-sharing sites. From there it was converted into a torrent which lay mostly dormant. It took me six weeks to download this file. I'll seed it as long as I can. 

If anyone can point me in the direction of a high-quality copy for sale, I'd greatly appreciate it
